      • moveSacFile

        public void moveSacFile(java.util.function.Predicate<SACFileName> predicate,
                        java.nio.file.Path movePath,
                        java.nio.file.CopyOption... options)
                 throws java.io.IOException
        Move sacfiles which satisfies an input sacPredicate. For example, if you want to move all synthetic sac files,

        predicate is sfn → sfn.isSYN()

        パラメータ:
        predicate - Sac files satisfying the sacPredicate will be moved.
        movePath - Path of a trash
        options - for copying
        例外:
        java.io.IOException - if an I/O error occurs

      • sacFileSet

        戻り値:
        unmodifiable Set of all SAC files in this including observed, synthetic and partial derivatives.
        例外:
        java.io.IOException - if an I/O error occurs
